---
title: Lebanese Beef Skewers with Herby Quinoa Tabbouleh
description: Tabbouleh—a famous Lebanese dish —is a delightfully herbaceous grain salad. We’re keeping it traditional with parsley, cucumber, and tomato, but changing things up with nutty quinoa in lieu of bulgur. Topped with cinnamon, allspice, and cayenne-spiked meatball skewers, you’ll be instantly transported to Beirut.
